'''德米特里·約瑟福維奇·伊凡諾夫斯基'''（{{lang-ru|Ивановский, Дмитрий Иосифович}}，1864年10月28日-1920年6月20日）是一位[[俄國|俄國]][[植物學家|植物學家]]，是[[病毒|病毒]]的可濾性的發現者（1892年）和[[病毒學|病毒學]]的創始人之一。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Lechevalier |first=Hubert |year=1972 |title=Dmitri Iosifovich Ivanovski (1864–-1920) |journal=Bacteriological Reviews |volume=36 |issue=2 |pages=135–-45 |publisher=American Society for Microbiology |location=Washington, D.C. |issn=0005-3678 |pmid=4557165 |url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC408320/pdf/bactrev00200-0002.pdf |language=en |format= |accessdate=October 16, 2011 |pmc=408320 |archive-date=2020-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413083320/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC408320/pdf/bactrev00200-0002.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="levine">{{cite journal |journal=[[J_Virol|J Virol]] |date=1992 August |volume=66 |issue=8 |pages=4629–31 |pmc=241285 |pmid=1629947 |title=One hundred years of virology |author=A Lustig and A J Levine }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 =Bos| first1 = L. | year = 1995 | title = The Embryonic Beginning of Virology: Unbiased Thinking and Dogmatic Stagnation | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-virology_1995_140_3/page/613| journal = Archives of Virology | volume = 140 | pages = 613–-619 | issn = 03048608}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| last = Zaitlin| first = Milton| editor1-last = Kung| editor1-first = S. D.| editor2-last = Yang| editor2-first = S. F.| title = Discoveries in Plant Biology| year = 1998| publisher = World Publishing Co.| location = Hong Kong| isbn = 978-981-02-1313-8| pages = 105–-110| chapter = The Discovery of the Causal Agent of the Tobacco Mosaic Disease| chapterurl = http://www.apsnet.org/publications/apsnetfeatures/Documents/1998/ZaitlinDiscoveryCausalAgentTobaccoMosaicVirus.pdf| access-date = 2013-05-07| archive-date = 2012-02-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120204055328/http://www.apsnet.org/publications/apsnetfeatures/Documents/1998/ZaitlinDiscoveryCausalAgentTobaccoMosaicVirus.pdf| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Sebastion|first=Anton|title=A dictionary of the history of science|publisher=Informa Health Care|location=Google Books Excerpt|year=2001|isbn=1-85070-418-X|oclc=9781850704188|url=http://books.google.com/?id=gTXFN-8v95MC&pg=PA267&dq=Dmitry+Iosifovich+Ivanovsky|accessdate=2008-10-24|language=en|page=267}}</ref>

伊凡諾夫斯基求學于[[聖彼得堡大學|聖彼得堡大學]]，1887年被送往[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]和[[比薩拉比亞|比薩拉比亞]]研究當時造成了極大危害的[[菸草|菸草]]疾病。三年之後，他又被送往[[克里米亞|克里米亞]]調查同樣的事。他發現這些疾病都是由極小的感染源造成的，并利用[[尚柏朗濾器|尚柏朗濾器]]確認了這一事實，1892年他在一篇文章中描述了其發現，<ref>{{cite journal | last = Iwanowski | first = D. | title = Über die Mosaikkrankheit der Tabakspflanze | journal = Bulletin Scientifique publié par l'Académie Impériale des Sciences de Saint-Pétersbourg / Nouvelle Serie III | volume = 35 | pages = 67–-70 | location = St. Petersburg | date = 1892 | language=de,ru}} Translated into English in Johnson, J., Ed. (1942) ''Phytopathological classics'' (St. Paul, Minnesota: American Phytopathological Society) No. 7, pp. 27–-30.</ref> 1902年將之寫成專題論文。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Iwanowski | first = D. | title = Über die Mosaikkrankheit der Tabakspflanze | journal = Zeitschrift fur Pflanzenkranheiten und Pflanzenschutz | volume = 13 | pages = 1–-41 | date = 1903 | language = de | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=iG0oAQAAIAAJ&pg=PR13#v=onepage&q&f=false | access-date = 2013-05-07 | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126084434/https://books.google.com/books?id=iG0oAQAAIAAJ&pg=PR13#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>

1898年，德國微生物學家[[馬丁烏斯·貝杰林克|馬丁烏斯·貝杰林克]]獨自再次完成了伊凡諾夫斯基的相關實驗，并確認用濾器確實過濾出了新的一種感染源，並將之命名為[[病毒|病毒]]。貝杰林克後來也承認了是伊凡諾夫斯基先於他得出了相同結論。<ref name="levine"></ref>

